The species find attractiveness in their tail feathers instead of faces like we do, since their faces are mostly the same. They can have many features like flowers growing off of them, moss, bush-like hair, vines, and more natural features. They also have leaves for facial hair

They don't have organs and their heart is replaced with a root core which controls the spread of nutrients throughout the body, in their society there are three genders they are born into and due to having three genders their relationships consist of three people instead of two
